{
  "openapi": "3.0.3",
  "info": {
    "title": "Hypedexer Live Data — WebSocket API",
    "version": "0.1.0",
    "description": "WebSocket API for real-time Hyperliquid live data streaming.\n\n## Connection\n\n```\nwss://enterprise.hypedexer.com/ws?token=<API_KEY>\n```\n\nThe `token` query parameter is optional (only required when `API_KEY` is configured on the server).\n\nOn successful connection, the server sends:\n```json\n{\"type\": \"connected\"}\n```\n\nIf the token is invalid:\n```json\n{\"type\": \"error\", \"message\": \"Invalid API key\"}\n```\n\n## Protocol\n\nAll messages are JSON. The client sends **subscribe**, **unsubscribe**, and **pong** messages. The server sends **acknowledgements**, **snapshots**, and **real-time updates**.\n\nBoth `\"method\"` and `\"type\"` fields are accepted as the message type discriminator (e.g., `{\"method\": \"subscribe\", ...}` and `{\"type\": \"subscribe\", ...}` are equivalent).\n\n## Supported subscriptions\n\n| Type | Required params | Description |\n|------|----------------|-------------|\n| `userFills` | `user` | Fills for a specific user (snapshot + updates) |\n| `allFills` | — | All fills globally |\n| `allMids` | — | Mid prices for all coins (polled every 300ms) |\n| `trades` | — | Trade events |\n| `l2Book` | `coin` | L2 order book (snapshot + updates via Redis pub/sub) |\n| `l4Book` | `coin` | L4 raw order book (snapshot + updates via Redis pub/sub) |\n| `l4BookUpdates` | — | L4 book update events |\n\n## Acknowledgement formats\n\n**userFills & allMids** use `subscriptionResponse`:\n```json\n{\"channel\": \"subscriptionResponse\", \"data\": {\"method\": \"subscribe\", \"subscription\": {...}}}\n```\n\n**All other types** use `subscriptionUpdate`:\n```json\n{\"type\": \"subscriptionUpdate\", \"subscription\": {...}, \"active\": true}\n```\n\n## Data sources\n\n| Subscription | Source |\n|-------------|--------|\n| `userFills` | Redis pub/sub `userfills:{address}` |\n| `allMids` | Redis cache polling (0.3s interval, only sends on change) |\n| `l2Book` | Redis pub/sub `l2book:{coin}` |\n| `l4Book` / `l4BookUpdates` | Redis pub/sub `l4raw:{coin}` |\n| `allFills`, `trades` | Volume file streaming |",
    "contact": {
      "name": "Hypedexer"
    }
  },
  "servers": [
    {
      "url": "wss://enterprise.hypedexer.com",
      "description": "Production (WebSocket)"
    }
  ],
  "tags": [
    {
      "name": "WebSocket",
      "description": "Single multiplex endpoint `GET /ws` — subscribe and unsubscribe via JSON messages. Message schemas are documented under **components/schemas**."
    }
  ],
  "paths": {
    "/ws": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["WebSocket"],
        "operationId": "liveDataWebSocket",
        "summary": "WebSocket endpoint",
        "description": "Upgrade to WebSocket. After connection, send subscribe/unsubscribe JSON messages to start/stop receiving real-time data.",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "token",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string"
            },
            "description": "API key for authentication (optional, only required when API_KEY is configured)"
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "101": {
            "description": "WebSocket upgrade successful. Server sends `{\"type\": \"connected\"}` immediately."
          },
          "401": {
            "description": "Invalid or missing API key when authentication is required."
          }
        },
        "security": [
          {
            "TokenQuery": []
          }
        ],
        "x-websocket": true
      }
    }
  },
  "components": {
    "securitySchemes": {
      "TokenQuery": {
        "type": "apiKey",
        "in": "query",
        "name": "token",
        "description": "Optional API key when the server requires authentication (`wss://.../ws?token=<API_KEY>`)."
      }
    },
    "schemas": {
      "ClientMessage": {
        "description": "Any message sent by the client to the server. The `method` field (or `type` field, both accepted) determines the action.",
        "oneOf": [
          { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/SubscribeMessage" },
          { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/UnsubscribeMessage" },
          { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/PongMessage" }
        ]
      },
      "SubscribeMessage": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "Subscribe to a data channel. After subscribing, the server sends an acknowledgement and an initial snapshot (if applicable), then real-time updates.",
        "required": [
          "method",
          "subscription"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "method": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "`subscribe` (also accepted via the `type` field)",
            "enum": [
              "subscribe"
            ]
          },
          "subscription": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/SubscriptionParams"
          }
        },
        "example": {
          "method": "subscribe",
          "subscription": {
            "type": "userFills",
            "user": "0xabc..."
          }
        }
      },
      "UnsubscribeMessage": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "Unsubscribe from a data channel. The server sends an acknowledgement.",
        "required": [
          "method",
          "subscription"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "method": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "unsubscribe"
            ]
          },
          "subscription": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/SubscriptionParams"
          }
        },
        "example": {
          "method": "unsubscribe",
          "subscription": {
            "type": "userFills",
            "user": "0xabc..."
          }
        }
      },
      "PongMessage": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "Client heartbeat response. Send this in response to server pings to keep the connection alive.",
        "required": [
          "method"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "method": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "pong"
            ]
          }
        },
        "example": {
          "method": "pong"
        }
      },
      "SubscriptionParams": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "Parameters for a subscription. The `type` field selects the data channel. Additional fields are required depending on the type.",
        "required": [
          "type"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "type": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Subscription type",
            "enum": [
              "userFills",
              "allFills",
              "allMids",
              "trades",
              "l2Book",
              "l4Book",
              "l4BookUpdates"
            ]
          },
          "user": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Ethereum address (0x-prefixed). **Required** for `userFills`."
          },
          "coin": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Coin symbol (e.g., `BTC`). **Required** for `l2Book` and `l4Book`."
          },
          "coins": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "type": "string"
            },
            "description": "List of coin symbols (optional, for future use)"
          },
          "dex": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "DEX filter for `allMids`. Omit for perps only, `ALL_DEXS` for all, or a specific DEX name."
          },
          "aggregateByTime": {
            "type": "boolean",
            "description": "When true, fills with the same timestamp are aggregated: sizes summed, prices weighted-averaged. Only applies to `userFills`.",
            "default": false
          }
        }
      },
      "ServerConnected": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "Sent immediately after a successful WebSocket connection.",
        "properties": {
          "type": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "connected"
            ]
          }
        },
        "example": {
          "type": "connected"
        }
      },
      "ServerError": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "Error message from the server.",
        "properties": {
          "type": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "error"
            ]
          },
          "message": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Human-readable error description"
          }
        },
        "example": {
          "type": "error",
          "message": "Unsupported subscription: unknownType"
        }
      },
      "SubscriptionResponseAck": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "Acknowledgement sent for `userFills` and `allMids` subscriptions (subscribe and unsubscribe).",
        "properties": {
          "channel": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "subscriptionResponse"
            ]
          },
          "data": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
              "method": {
                "type": "string",
                "enum": [
                  "subscribe",
                  "unsubscribe"
                ],
                "description": "The action that was acknowledged"
              },
              "subscription": {
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/SubscriptionParams"
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "example": {
          "channel": "subscriptionResponse",
          "data": {
            "method": "subscribe",
            "subscription": {
              "type": "userFills",
              "user": "0xabc...",
              "aggregateByTime": false
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "SubscriptionUpdateAck": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "Acknowledgement sent for `allFills`, `trades`, `l2Book`, `l4Book`, and `l4BookUpdates` subscriptions.",
        "properties": {
          "type": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "subscriptionUpdate"
            ]
          },
          "subscription": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/SubscriptionParams"
          },
          "active": {
            "type": "boolean",
            "description": "`true` on subscribe, `false` on unsubscribe"
          }
        },
        "example": {
          "type": "subscriptionUpdate",
          "subscription": {
            "type": "l2Book",
            "coin": "BTC"
          },
          "active": true
        }
      },
      "UserFillsSnapshot": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "Initial snapshot of user fills, sent immediately after subscribing to `userFills`. Contains `isSnapshot: true`.",
        "properties": {
          "channel": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "userFills"
            ]
          },
          "data": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
              "isSnapshot": {
                "type": "boolean",
                "description": "Always `true` for the initial snapshot",
                "enum": [
                  true
                ]
              },
              "user": {
                "type": "string",
                "description": "Ethereum address (lowercase)"
              },
              "fills": {
                "type": "array",
                "items": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Fill"
                },
                "description": "Historical fills for this user. If `aggregateByTime` is enabled, fills with the same timestamp are aggregated."
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "example": {
          "channel": "userFills",
          "data": {
            "isSnapshot": true,
            "user": "0xabc...",
            "fills": [
              {
                "coin": "BTC",
                "px": "65000.5",
                "sz": "0.1",
                "side": "B",
                "time": 1700000050000,
                "startPosition": "0.0",
                "dir": "Open Long",
                "closedPnl": "0.0",
                "hash": "0x...",
                "oid": 12345,
                "crossed": true,
                "fee": "1.625",
                "tid": 67890,
                "feeToken": "USDC"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "UserFillsUpdate": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "Real-time fill update for a subscribed user. Received via Redis pub/sub `userfills:{address}`.",
        "properties": {
          "channel": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "userFills"
            ]
          },
          "data": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
              "user": {
                "type": "string",
                "description": "Ethereum address (lowercase)"
              },
              "fills": {
                "type": "array",
                "items": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Fill"
                },
                "description": "New fills. If `aggregateByTime` is enabled, fills with the same timestamp are aggregated."
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "example": {
          "channel": "userFills",
          "data": {
            "user": "0xabc...",
            "fills": [
              {
                "coin": "ETH",
                "px": "2500.0",
                "sz": "1.0",
                "side": "A",
                "time": 1700000090000
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "AllMidsSnapshot": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "Initial mid prices snapshot, sent immediately after subscribing to `allMids`.",
        "properties": {
          "channel": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "allMids"
            ]
          },
          "data": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
              "mids": {
                "type": "object",
                "additionalProperties": {
                  "type": "string"
                },
                "description": "Map of coin symbol to mid price string"
              },
              "dex": {
                "type": "string",
                "description": "Present when a DEX filter was specified in the subscription"
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "example": {
          "channel": "allMids",
          "data": {
            "mids": {
              "BTC": "66764.5",
              "ETH": "3421.2",
              "SOL": "150.75"
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "AllMidsUpdate": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "Mid prices update. Only sent when at least one mid price has changed since the last update. Polled every 300ms.",
        "properties": {
          "channel": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "allMids"
            ]
          },
          "data": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
              "mids": {
                "type": "object",
                "additionalProperties": {
                  "type": "string"
                },
                "description": "Full map of all current mid prices (not a diff)"
              },
              "dex": {
                "type": "string",
                "description": "Present when a DEX filter is active"
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "example": {
          "channel": "allMids",
          "data": {
            "mids": {
              "BTC": "66780.0",
              "ETH": "3425.5"
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "L2BookSnapshot": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "L2 order book snapshot, sent immediately after subscribing to `l2Book` (if data is available in Redis cache).",
        "properties": {
          "channel": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "l2Book"
            ]
          },
          "data": {
            "type": "object",
            "description": "L2 book data as received from Redis cache",
            "properties": {
              "coin": {
                "type": "string"
              },
              "bids": {
                "type": "array",
                "items": {
                  "type": "array",
                  "items": {
                    "type": "string"
                  },
                  "description": "[price, size]"
                }
              },
              "asks": {
                "type": "array",
                "items": {
                  "type": "array",
                  "items": {
                    "type": "string"
                  },
                  "description": "[price, size]"
                }
              },
              "timestamp": {
                "type": "integer",
                "nullable": true
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "example": {
          "channel": "l2Book",
          "data": {
            "coin": "BTC",
            "bids": [
              [
                "65000.0",
                "0.5"
              ],
              [
                "64999.0",
                "1.0"
              ]
            ],
            "asks": [
              [
                "65001.0",
                "0.3"
              ],
              [
                "65002.0",
                "0.7"
              ]
            ],
            "timestamp": 1700000050000
          }
        }
      },
      "L2BookUpdate": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "L2 order book update received via Redis pub/sub `l2book:{coin}`.",
        "properties": {
          "channel": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "l2Book"
            ]
          },
          "data": {
            "type": "object",
            "description": "L2 book update data as received from Redis"
          }
        },
        "example": {
          "channel": "l2Book",
          "data": {
            "coin": "BTC",
            "bids": [
              [
                "65000.5",
                "0.6"
              ]
            ],
            "asks": [
              [
                "65001.5",
                "0.4"
              ]
            ],
            "timestamp": 1700000051000
          }
        }
      },
      "L4BookSnapshot": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "L4 (raw) order book snapshot, sent immediately after subscribing to `l4Book` (if data is available in Redis cache).",
        "properties": {
          "channel": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "l4Book"
            ]
          },
          "data": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
              "snapshot": {
                "type": "object",
                "description": "L4 book snapshot data as received from Redis cache"
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "example": {
          "channel": "l4Book",
          "data": {
            "snapshot": {
              "coin": "BTC",
              "levels": []
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "L4BookUpdate": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "L4 order book update received via Redis pub/sub `l4raw:{coin}`. Contains raw book diff updates.",
        "properties": {
          "channel": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "l4Book"
            ]
          },
          "data": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
              "updates": {
                "type": "array",
                "description": "Array of L4 book diff events",
                "items": {
                  "type": "object",
                  "properties": {
                    "coin": {
                      "type": "string"
                    },
                    "side": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "enum": [
                        "A",
                        "B"
                      ]
                    },
                    "px": {
                      "type": "string"
                    },
                    "sz": {
                      "type": "string"
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "example": {
          "channel": "l4Book",
          "data": {
            "updates": [
              {
                "coin": "BTC",
                "side": "A",
                "px": "65001.0",
                "sz": "0.5"
              },
              {
                "coin": "BTC",
                "side": "B",
                "px": "64999.0",
                "sz": "0.3"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "AllFillsUpdate": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "Global fill event. Broadcast to all `allFills` subscribers.",
        "properties": {
          "channel": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "allFills"
            ]
          },
          "data": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "type": "object",
              "properties": {
                "address": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "description": "Ethereum address"
                },
                "fill": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Fill"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "TradesUpdate": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "Trade event. Broadcast to all `trades` subscribers.",
        "properties": {
          "channel": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "trades"
            ]
          },
          "data": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "type": "object",
              "properties": {
                "coin": {
                  "type": "string"
                },
                "px": {
                  "type": "string"
                },
                "sz": {
                  "type": "string"
                },
                "time": {
                  "type": "integer"
                },
                "side": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "enum": [
                    "A",
                    "B"
                  ]
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "Fill": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "A single fill from the Hyperliquid fullnode",
        "properties": {
          "coin": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Coin symbol",
            "example": "BTC"
          },
          "px": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Execution price",
            "example": "65000.5"
          },
          "sz": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Size",
            "example": "0.1"
          },
          "side": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "A",
              "B"
            ],
            "description": "A = ask (sell), B = bid (buy)"
          },
          "time": {
            "type": "integer",
            "description": "Timestamp in milliseconds since epoch",
            "example": 1700000050000
          },
          "startPosition": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Position before this fill",
            "example": "0.0"
          },
          "dir": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Direction description",
            "example": "Open Long"
          },
          "closedPnl": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Closed PnL from this fill",
            "example": "0.0"
          },
          "hash": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Transaction hash",
            "example": "0x..."
          },
          "oid": {
            "type": "integer",
            "description": "Order ID",
            "example": 12345
          },
          "crossed": {
            "type": "boolean",
            "description": "Whether the order crossed the spread"
          },
          "fee": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Fee amount",
            "example": "1.625"
          },
          "tid": {
            "type": "integer",
            "description": "Trade ID",
            "example": 67890
          },
          "feeToken": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Fee token symbol",
            "example": "USDC"
          }
        }
      },
      "ServerMessage": {
        "description": "Any message the server may send to the client",
        "oneOf": [
          {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ServerConnected"
          },
          {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ServerError"
          },
          {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/SubscriptionResponseAck"
          },
          {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/SubscriptionUpdateAck"
          },
          {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/UserFillsSnapshot"
          },
          {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/UserFillsUpdate"
          },
          {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/AllMidsSnapshot"
          },
          {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/AllMidsUpdate"
          },
          {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/L2BookSnapshot"
          },
          {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/L2BookUpdate"
          },
          {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/L4BookSnapshot"
          },
          {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/L4BookUpdate"
          },
          {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/AllFillsUpdate"
          },
          {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/TradesUpdate"
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  },
  "security": [
    {
      "TokenQuery": []
    }
  ]
}
